sent.orig: Caterpillars change into butterflies; Tadpoles change into froggies; And gorillas change into people.
sent.trans: 毛毛虫变成蝴蝶；蝌蚪变成小青蛙；还有大猩猩变成人。

sent.orig: He tried putting teeth into milk, into water, and into cell-culture medium.
sent.trans: 他尝试着把牙齿放入牛奶、水和细胞培养液中。

sent.orig: Turn scars into stars. Turn victims into victors. Turn zeros into heroes.
sent.trans: 化伤疤为明星。化牺牲为胜利。化虚无为英雄。

sent.orig: People weave thread into cloth,straw into hats,and reeds into baskets.
sent.trans: 人们把线织成布，把草编成草帽，把芦苇编成篮子。
